  "detailed_description": "<h1>Live streaming and postings on Youtube, Twitch, and SNS.</h1><p>Please see the Steam discussion boards page.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drive a Kei Truck through a collapsing Japan! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are being chased by aliens! Dodge attacks! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/6ca0dbcbd639acd16935542fa601f44e.poster.avif?t=1765942544\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/6ca0dbcbd639acd16935542fa601f44e.webm?t=1765942544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/6ca0dbcbd639acd16935542fa601f44e.mp4?t=1765942544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dodge attacks with wall-riding!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It is very dangerous to actually run in this way, so please do not imitate it!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/ecad5d6dd6383bbe955dfd522a7ea8b6.poster.avif?t=1765942544\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/ecad5d6dd6383bbe955dfd522a7ea8b6.webm?t=1765942544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/ecad5d6dd6383bbe955dfd522a7ea8b6.mp4?t=1765942544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recover the nitro by destruction!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I don't know why nitro is recovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/ec270744187b2013f9f6534f178b6e94.poster.avif?t=1765942544\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/ec270744187b2013f9f6534f178b6e94.webm?t=1765942544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/ec270744187b2013f9f6534f178b6e94.mp4?t=1765942544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Counterattack on enemies!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/00db98da6f4da690443d312a31b3928b.poster.avif?t=1765942544\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/00db98da6f4da690443d312a31b3928b.webm?t=1765942544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/00db98da6f4da690443d312a31b3928b.mp4?t=1765942544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle with giant creatures!  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/79a7116c280a005faee5bbdd5dd6bff9.poster.avif?t=1765942544\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/79a7116c280a005faee5bbdd5dd6bff9.webm?t=1765942544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556010/extras/79a7116c280a005faee5bbdd5dd6bff9.mp4?t=1765942544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game progression is based on a stage-by-stage system.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are stages where smaller enemies appear and stages where you fight giant bosses. There are stages where no enemies appear. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Compete with other players on online leaderboards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game implements online leaderboards, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >where scores and times are recorded for each stage so that you can compete with other players.</p>",
